vote.title:
A public hearing to receive comments regarding an application for and an ordinance granting a Planned Development District for IR Industrial Research District uses and general merchandise or food store greater than 3,500 square feet use on property zoned an IR Industrial Research District on the west corner of Mockingbird Lane and Maple Avenue
Recommendation of Staff:  Denial
Recommendation of CPC:  Approval, subject to a conceptual plan, Phase I development plan and conditions
Z189-304(CY)
